name: Samuel Lee
summary: Samuel Lee, a 32-year-old software developer from San Francisco currently based in Los Angeles, speaks English, Spanish, and Korean. He's a physically active, gay East Asian man who enjoys coding, CrossFit, traveling, cooking, and reading. He is an agnostic liberal who values honesty, kindness, and ambition. A man of intellect, Samuel holds a graduate degree from the University of Chicago and identifies as an ENTJ on the Myers-Briggs Type Indicator. Though he currently does not have children, he is open to having them in the future. He's a fan of dogs but not a fan of smoking or drug use. He enjoys a drink occasionally and is looking for a gay man aged 26 to 38 who shares similar values and life goals, is physically active, comfortable with occasional drinking but not into smoking or drugs.
